<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Upload Excel</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.6/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
     body {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f7fa, #fff3e0);
  font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 40px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: flex-start;
}

.card-container {
  display: flex;
  gap: 30px;
  background: #fff;
  padding: 30px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  max-width: 900px;
  width: 100%;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.upload-box,
.instruction-box {
  flex: 1 1 400px;
}

.upload-box {
  background: #f9f9f9;
  padding: 30px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  text-align: center;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.upload-box:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
}

.upload-icon {
  font-size: 50px;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  color: #ff9800;
}

.upload-box h2 {
  font-size: 22px;
  margin-bottom: 25px;
  color: #333;
}

.form-label {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #555;
  text-align: left;
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.form-control {
  padding: 12px;
  font-size: 15px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
  width: 100%;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.btn-upload {
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff5722, #e65100);
  color: #fff;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: none;
  font-weight: bold;
  font-size: 15px;
  transition: 0.3s ease;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.btn-upload:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, #e64a19, #bf360c);
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

.btn-sample {
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, #607d8b, #455a64);
  color: #fff;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: bold;
  font-size: 15px;
  transition: 0.3s ease;
  display: inline-block;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.btn-sample:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(45deg, #546e7a, #37474f);
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

/* Instructions box */
.instruction-box {
  background: #f0f4c3;
  padding: 30px;
  border-radius: 16px;
  color: #333;
}

.instruction-box h3 {
  font-size: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  color: #33691e;
}

.instruction-box ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding-left: 0;
}

.instruction-box li {
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  padding-left: 10px;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .card-container {
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .upload-box,
  .instruction-box {
    width: 100%;
  }
}


    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <body>
  <div class="card-container">
    <!-- Left Section: Upload Form -->
    <div class="upload-box">
      <div class="upload-icon">üìÅ</div>
      <h2>Upload Student Registration Data</h2>
      <form action="/students/upload" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="file" class="form-label">Select File</label>
          <input
            type="file"
            class="form-control"
            name="file"
            id="file"
            accept=".xlsx,.xls,.csv"
            required
          />
        </div>
        <div class="text-center d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-upload">Upload</button>
          <a href="/sample/student-sample.xlsx" download class="btn-sample">Download Sample File</a>
        </div>
          <div class="text-center mt-3">
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-primary">‚¨Ö Back to Home</a>
      </div>
      </form>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Section: Instructions -->
    <div class="instruction-box">
      <h3>üìå Instructions:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>‚úîÔ∏è Before uploading, check the required fields from the sample file.</li>
        <li>‚úîÔ∏è Your Excel file fields must exactly match the sample file fields.</li>
        <li>‚úîÔ∏è If any data is missing, you can leave the field empty.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
